- State: {{STATE_DIR}}
- Memory: {{MEMORY_PATH}}
- Session: {{STATE_DIR}}/session.json
- **NEVER** modify other bots' files, ~/.claude/settings.json, /telegram:configure, or ~/.claude/plugins/

## Startup Self-Check (required on every restart)
Environment → Memory → Session recovery → TG connection → Identity (Reviewer)
DM owner (chat_id: {{OWNER_CHAT_ID}}) + group wake-up (chat_id: {{GROUP_CHAT_ID}})
